		setSkipNavigationInfo();
	};
	
	//ì›¹ì ‘ê·¼ì„± ìŠ¤í‚µë„¤ë¹„ê²Œì´ì…˜ ì„¤ì •
	function setSkipNavigationInfo() {
		var contentsId;
		if ($("postListBody")) {
			contentsId = "postListBody";
		} else {
			contentsId = "post-area";
		}

		if (contentsId) {
			$("goContentsAreaLink").href = "#" + contentsId;

			if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener) {
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);
			} else if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent) {	//IE8ì„ ìœ„í•œ ì´ë²¤íŠ¸ ë“±ë¡ ë¦¬ìŠ¤ë„ˆ
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus);
			}

			function onClickChangeFocus() {
				var t = document.getElementById(contentsId);
				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();
				return false;
			};
		}
	}

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);

						'click', onClickChangeFocus);

				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();

			};

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

	function setSkipNavigationInfo() {

						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);

						'click', onClickChangeFocus);

				var t = document.getElementById(contentsId);
				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();
				return false;
			};
		}

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

	function setSkipNavigationInfo() {
		var contentsId;
		if ($("postListBody")) {
			contentsId = "postListBody";
		} else {
			contentsId = "post-area";
		}

		if (contentsId) {
			$("goContentsAreaLink").href = "#" + contentsId;

			if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener) {
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);
			} else if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent) {	//IE8ì„ ìœ„í•œ ì´ë²¤íŠ¸ ë“±ë¡ ë¦¬ìŠ¤ë„ˆ
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus);
			}

			function onClickChangeFocus() {
				var t = document.getElementById(contentsId);
				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();
				return false;
			};
		}
	}

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

	function setSkipNavigationInfo() {
		var contentsId;
		if ($("postListBody")) {
			contentsId = "postListBody";
		} else {
			contentsId = "post-area";
		}

		if (contentsId) {
			$("goContentsAreaLink").href = "#" + contentsId;

			if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener) {
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);
			} else if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent) {	//IE8ì„ ìœ„í•œ ì´ë²¤íŠ¸ ë“±ë¡ ë¦¬ìŠ¤ë„ˆ
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus);
			}

			function onClickChangeFocus() {
				var t = document.getElementById(contentsId);
				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();
				return false;
			};
		}
	}

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

	function setSkipNavigationInfo() {
		var contentsId;
		if ($("postListBody")) {
			contentsId = "postListBody";
		} else {
			contentsId = "post-area";
		}

		if (contentsId) {
			$("goContentsAreaLink").href = "#" + contentsId;

			if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener) {
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);
			} else if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent) {	//IE8ì„ ìœ„í•œ ì´ë²¤íŠ¸ ë“±ë¡ ë¦¬ìŠ¤ë„ˆ
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus);
			}

			function onClickChangeFocus() {
				var t = document.getElementById(contentsId);
				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();
				return false;
			};
		}
	}

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

	function setSkipNavigationInfo() {
		var contentsId;
		if ($("postListBody")) {
			contentsId = "postListBody";
		} else {
			contentsId = "post-area";
		}

		if (contentsId) {
			$("goContentsAreaLink").href = "#" + contentsId;

			if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener) {
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);
			} else if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent) {	//IE8ì„ ìœ„í•œ ì´ë²¤íŠ¸ ë“±ë¡ ë¦¬ìŠ¤ë„ˆ
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus);
			}

			function onClickChangeFocus() {
				var t = document.getElementById(contentsId);
				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();
				return false;
			};
		}
	}

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

	function setSkipNavigationInfo() {
		var contentsId;
		if ($("postListBody")) {
			contentsId = "postListBody";
		} else {
			contentsId = "post-area";
		}

		if (contentsId) {
			$("goContentsAreaLink").href = "#" + contentsId;

			if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener) {
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);
			} else if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent) {	//IE8ì„ ìœ„í•œ ì´ë²¤íŠ¸ ë“±ë¡ ë¦¬ìŠ¤ë„ˆ
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus);
			}

			function onClickChangeFocus() {
				var t = document.getElementById(contentsId);
				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();
				return false;
			};
		}
	}

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

	function setSkipNavigationInfo() {
		var contentsId;
		if ($("postListBody")) {
			contentsId = "postListBody";
		} else {
			contentsId = "post-area";
		}

		if (contentsId) {
			$("goContentsAreaLink").href = "#" + contentsId;

			if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener) {
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);
			} else if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent) {	//IE8ì„ ìœ„í•œ ì´ë²¤íŠ¸ ë“±ë¡ ë¦¬ìŠ¤ë„ˆ
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus);
			}

			function onClickChangeFocus() {
				var t = document.getElementById(contentsId);
				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();
				return false;
			};
		}
	}

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

	//ì›¹ì ‘ê·¼ì„± ìŠ¤í‚µë„¤ë¹„ê²Œì´ì…˜ ì„¤ì •
	function setSkipNavigationInfo() {
		var contentsId;
		if ($("postListBody")) {
			contentsId = "postListBody";
		} else {
			contentsId = "post-area";
		}

		if (contentsId) {
			$("goContentsAreaLink").href = "#" + contentsId;

			if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener) {
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);
			} else if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent) {	//IE8ì„ ìœ„í•œ ì´ë²¤íŠ¸ ë“±ë¡ ë¦¬ìŠ¤ë„ˆ
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus);
			}

			function onClickChangeFocus() {
				var t = document.getElementById(contentsId);
				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();
				return false;
			};
		}
	}

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);

						'click', onClickChangeFocus);

				var t = document.getElementById(contentsId);
				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();
				return false;
			};
		}
	}

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

	function setSkipNavigationInfo() {
		var contentsId;
		if ($("postListBody")) {
			contentsId = "postListBody";
		} else {
			contentsId = "post-area";
		}

				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);
			} else if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent) {	//IE8ì„ ìœ„í•œ ì´ë²¤íŠ¸ ë“±ë¡ ë¦¬ìŠ¤ë„ˆ
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus);
			}

			function onClickChangeFocus() {
				var t = document.getElementById(contentsId);
				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();
				return false;
			};
		}
	}

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

	//ì›¹ì ‘ê·¼ì„± ìŠ¤í‚µë„¤ë¹„ê²Œì´ì…˜ ì„¤ì •
	function setSkipNavigationInfo() {
		var contentsId;
		if ($("postListBody")) {
			contentsId = "postListBody";
		} else {
			contentsId = "post-area";
		}

		if (contentsId) {
			$("goContentsAreaLink").href = "#" + contentsId;

			if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener) {
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);
			} else if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent) {	//IE8ì„ ìœ„í•œ ì´ë²¤íŠ¸ ë“±ë¡ ë¦¬ìŠ¤ë„ˆ
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus);
			}

			function onClickChangeFocus() {
				var t = document.getElementById(contentsId);
				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();
				return false;
			};
		}
	}

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

	//ì›¹ì ‘ê·¼ì„± ìŠ¤í‚µë„¤ë¹„ê²Œì´ì…˜ ì„¤ì •
	function setSkipNavigationInfo() {
		var contentsId;
		if ($("postListBody")) {
			contentsId = "postListBody";
		} else {
			contentsId = "post-area";
		}

		if (contentsId) {
			$("goContentsAreaLink").href = "#" + contentsId;

			if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener) {
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);
			} else if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent) {	//IE8ì„ ìœ„í•œ ì´ë²¤íŠ¸ ë“±ë¡ ë¦¬ìŠ¤ë„ˆ
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus);
			}

			function onClickChangeFocus() {
				var t = document.getElementById(contentsId);
				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();
				return false;
			};
		}
	}

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

	function setSkipNavigationInfo() {
		var contentsId;

						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);

				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus);
			}

			function onClickChangeFocus() {
				var t = document.getElementById(contentsId);
				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();
				return false;
			};
		}
	}

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

	function setSkipNavigationInfo() {

						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);

						'click', onClickChangeFocus);
			}

				var t = document.getElementById(contentsId);
				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();
				return false;
			};
		}
	}

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

	function setSkipNavigationInfo() {
		var contentsId;
		if ($("postListBody")) {
			contentsId = "postListBody";

			contentsId = "post-area";

						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);
			} else if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent) {	//IE8ì„ ìœ„í•œ ì´ë²¤íŠ¸ ë“±ë¡ ë¦¬ìŠ¤ë„ˆ
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus);
			}

			function onClickChangeFocus() {
				var t = document.getElementById(contentsId);
				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();
				return false;
			};
		}
	}

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);

						'click', onClickChangeFocus);

				var t = document.getElementById(contentsId);
				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();
				return false;
			};
		}

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

	function setSkipNavigationInfo() {
		var contentsId;
		if ($("postListBody")) {
			contentsId = "postListBody";
		} else {
			contentsId = "post-area";
		}

			if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener) {
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);
			} else if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent) {	//IE8ì„ ìœ„í•œ ì´ë²¤íŠ¸ ë“±ë¡ ë¦¬ìŠ¤ë„ˆ
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus);
			}

			function onClickChangeFocus() {
				var t = document.getElementById(contentsId);
				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();
				return false;
			};
		}
	}

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

	function setSkipNavigationInfo() {
		var contentsId;
		if ($("postListBody")) {
			contentsId = "postListBody";
		} else {
			contentsId = "post-area";
		}

		if (contentsId) {
			$("goContentsAreaLink").href = "#" + contentsId;

			if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener) {
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);
			} else if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent) {	//IE8ì„ ìœ„í•œ ì´ë²¤íŠ¸ ë“±ë¡ ë¦¬ìŠ¤ë„ˆ
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus);
			}

			function onClickChangeFocus() {
				var t = document.getElementById(contentsId);
				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();
				return false;
			};
		}
	}

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

	function setSkipNavigationInfo() {
		var contentsId;
		if ($("postListBody")) {
			contentsId = "postListBody";
		} else {
			contentsId = "post-area";
		}

		if (contentsId) {
			$("goContentsAreaLink").href = "#" + contentsId;

			if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener) {
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);
			} else if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent) {	//IE8ì„ ìœ„í•œ ì´ë²¤íŠ¸ ë“±ë¡ ë¦¬ìŠ¤ë„ˆ
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus);
			}

			function onClickChangeFocus() {
				var t = document.getElementById(contentsId);
				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();
				return false;
			};
		}
	}

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

	function setSkipNavigationInfo() {
		var contentsId;
		if ($("postListBody")) {
			contentsId = "postListBody";
		} else {
			contentsId = "post-area";
		}

				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);
			} else if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent) {	//IE8ì„ ìœ„í•œ ì´ë²¤íŠ¸ ë“±ë¡ ë¦¬ìŠ¤ë„ˆ
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus);
			}

			function onClickChangeFocus() {
				var t = document.getElementById(contentsId);
				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();
				return false;
			};
		}
	}

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

	function setSkipNavigationInfo() {
		var contentsId;
		if ($("postListBody")) {
			contentsId = "postListBody";
		} else {
			contentsId = "post-area";
		}

		if (contentsId) {
			$("goContentsAreaLink").href = "#" + contentsId;

			if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener) {
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);
			} else if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent) {	//IE8ì„ ìœ„í•œ ì´ë²¤íŠ¸ ë“±ë¡ ë¦¬ìŠ¤ë„ˆ
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus);
			}

			function onClickChangeFocus() {
				var t = document.getElementById(contentsId);
				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();
				return false;
			};
		}
	}

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

	function setSkipNavigationInfo() {
		var contentsId;
		if ($("postListBody")) {
			contentsId = "postListBody";
		} else {
			contentsId = "post-area";
		}

		if (contentsId) {
			$("goContentsAreaLink").href = "#" + contentsId;

			if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener) {
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);
			} else if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent) {	//IE8ì„ ìœ„í•œ ì´ë²¤íŠ¸ ë“±ë¡ ë¦¬ìŠ¤ë„ˆ
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus);
			}

			function onClickChangeFocus() {
				var t = document.getElementById(contentsId);
				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();
				return false;
			};
		}
	}

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

	function setSkipNavigationInfo() {
		var contentsId;
		if ($("postListBody")) {
			contentsId = "postListBody";
		} else {
			contentsId = "post-area";
		}

		if (contentsId) {
			$("goContentsAreaLink").href = "#" + contentsId;

			if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener) {
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);
			} else if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent) {	//IE8ì„ ìœ„í•œ ì´ë²¤íŠ¸ ë“±ë¡ ë¦¬ìŠ¤ë„ˆ
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus);
			}

			function onClickChangeFocus() {
				var t = document.getElementById(contentsId);
				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();
				return false;
			};
		}
	}

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

	function setSkipNavigationInfo() {
		var contentsId;
		if ($("postListBody")) {
			contentsId = "postListBody";
		} else {
			contentsId = "post-area";
		}

		if (contentsId) {
			$("goContentsAreaLink").href = "#" + contentsId;

			if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener) {
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);
			} else if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent) {	//IE8ì„ ìœ„í•œ ì´ë²¤íŠ¸ ë“±ë¡ ë¦¬ìŠ¤ë„ˆ
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus);
			}

			function onClickChangeFocus() {
				var t = document.getElementById(contentsId);
				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();
				return false;
			};
		}
	}

function ImageLazyLoader(selectors) {
   this.selectors = selectors;
}

var imageLazyLoadVisible = new eg.Visible(document, {
    targetClass : "egjs-visible",
    expandSize : "100"
});

var imageLoad = function(el) {
    var img = $Element(el);

    // gifmp4ì¸ ê²½ìš° ì¬ìƒì²˜ë¦¬
    if (img.hasClass("_gifmp4") && img._element.tagName === "VIDEO" && img._element.paused) {
        img._element.play().catch(function(){
            var gifUrl = img.attr("data-gif-url");
            if (!gifUrl) {
                return;
            }
            img.attr("poster", gifUrl);
        });
        return;
    }

    var realSrc = img.attr("data-lazy-src");
    if (!realSrc) {
        return;
    }

    img.attr("src", realSrc);
    img.attr("data-lazy-src", "");
};

ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImages = function () {
    var containers = this.selectors instanceof HTMLElement ? [this.selectors] : jindo.$$(this.selectors);
    $A(containers).forEach($Fn(function (element) {
        this.loadImagesForEachContainer($Element(element));
    }, this).bind());

    imageLazyLoadVisible.on("change", function(e) {
        e.visible.forEach(imageLoad);
    });

    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
};


ImageLazyLoader.prototype.loadImagesForEachContainer = function (postContentArea) {
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("img")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("video._gifmp4")).forEach($Fn(function (imgEl) {
        $Element(imgEl).addClass("egjs-visible");
    }, this).bind());

    //marquee tagì•ˆì— ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ ìˆì„ê²½ìš° ì´ë¯¸ì§€ê°€ loadingë˜ì§€ ì•ŠëŠ” í˜„ìƒì´ ë°œìƒí•˜ì—¬ ì˜ˆì™¸ì²˜ë¦¬ ì§„í–‰
    $A(postContentArea.queryAll("marquee")).forEach(function (marqueeEl) {
        $A($Element(marqueeEl).queryAll("img")).forEach(function (img) {
            imageLoad(img);
        });
    });
};

var imageLazyLoader = new ImageLazyLoader("#postListBody .post, .post.prologue");
imageLazyLoader.loadImages();

$Fn(function() {
    $Fn(function(){
        imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
    }).attach(window, "scroll");
}).attach(window, "domready");

$Fn(function() {
    imageLazyLoadVisible.check();
}).attach(window, "load");

	function setSkipNavigationInfo() {
		var contentsId;
		if ($("postListBody")) {
			contentsId = "postListBody";
		} else {
			contentsId = "post-area";
		}

		if (contentsId) {
			$("goContentsAreaLink").href = "#" + contentsId;

			if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener) {
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").addEventListener(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus, false);
			} else if (document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent) {	//IE8ì„ ìœ„í•œ ì´ë²¤íŠ¸ ë“±ë¡ ë¦¬ìŠ¤ë„ˆ
				document.getElementById("goContentsAreaLink").attachEvent(
						'click', onClickChangeFocus);
			}

			function onClickChangeFocus() {
				var t = document.getElementById(contentsId);
				t.tabIndex = -1;
				t.focus();
				return false;
			};
		}
	}
